This paper deals with the problem of state and parameter estimation using recursive adaptive filtering methods, which is a common topic in the field of control systems (cs.SY). The paper also discusses matrix factorization methods such as SVD, which are often used in machine learning and data analysis (cs.LG, cs.AI). The use of numerical methods and algorithms for computation and optimization is also a key aspect of the paper, which falls under the categories of numerical analysis (cs.NA) and software engineering (cs.SE).
